## Day 2: Playing with Fire(crawler)
**Mood:** Amazed 🤯

Spent the evening testing the Firecrawler API. It is honestly black magic. I fed it a messy documentation URL, and it spit out perfectly structured Markdown. 

I used Postman to test the endpoint before bringing it into n8n:

```json
// The payload I sent to Firecrawler
{
  "url": "[https://example.com/docs](https://example.com/docs)",
  "pageOptions": {
    "onlyMainContent": true
  }
}
